<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      }

      header {
        background-color: #4b3c99;
        padding: 30px;
        color: white;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .large-title {
        padding: 0px 10px 0px 30px;
        font-size: 2em;
        font-weight: bolder;
      }

      .badge {
        background-color: #4b3c99;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
        height: 30px;
        padding: 0px 5px;
        padding-top: 6px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .main {
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .main .right {
        width: 475px;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 30px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 150px;
        background-color: #4b3c99;
      }

      .center {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .title {
        color: #888888;
      }

      .subtext {
        color: white;
      }

      .icons ul a {
        border: 1px solid white;
        border-radius: 7px;
        color: white;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        margin-right: 10px;
      }

      .icons ul a:hover {
        background-color: white;
        color: black;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .text {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .fine-print {
        padding: 30px 0px;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .fineprint .url {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .fine-print p {
        color: #9e9e9e;
        font-size: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="center">EDUCAD</header>
    <br /><br /><br />
    <div class="container">
      <a class="large-title">Application Received</a
      ><span class="badge">New</span>
    </div>

    <br />

    <div class="main">
      <div class="right">
        <a><b>We have received your application, you will be contacted shortly.</b></a
        ><br /><br />
        <a
          >Our team are working hard to ensure you get the best experience.
		  We will contact you shortly regarding the details you have inputted in our survey as followed:</a
        >
        <br /><br />
        <a class="title">Student Name</a><br />
        <a><b>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</b></a
        ><br /><br />
        <a class="title">Tuition Type</a><br />
        <a><b>{{tuitionType}}</b></a
        ><br /><br />
        <a class="title">Contact Number</a><br />
        <a><b>{{contactNumber}}</b></a
        ><br /><br />
      </div>
      <br />
	  <a>If you believe the information is incorrect, please submit another application on our website.</a><br /><br />
      <a>Thanks,</a><br />
      <a>System Message</a>
    </div>

    <div class="fine-print">
      <p>
        We will never send you an email asking for sensitive information such as
        bank or card details.<br />
        If you have received such an email it might be a scam email,
        <b>please contact us.</b>
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        This email is sent from an automated mailing server. We cannot respond
        to replies sent to this email address.<br />For more information please
        visit our <span class="url"><b>website</b>.</span>
      </p>
      <br />
      <p><b>Address:</b></p>
      <p>21 Patey Street, Manchester, England, M12 5RP</p>
    </div>

    <footer class="purple text-center text-white">
      <div class="container p-4 pb-0">
        <section class="mb-4">
          <a
            class="btn btn-outline-light btn-floating m-1"
            href="#!"
            role="button"
            ><i class="fa fa-facebook-f"></i
          ></a>
          <a
            class="btn btn-outline-light btn-floating m-1"
            href="#!"
            role="button"
            ><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i
          ></a>
          <a
            class="btn btn-outline-light btn-floating m-1"
            href="#!"
            role="button"
            ><i class="fa fa-google"></i
          ></a>
          <a
            class="btn btn-outline-light btn-floating m-1"
            href="#!"
            role="button"
            ><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i
          ></a>
        </section>
      </div>
      Copyright -
      <div class="text-center p-3">Educad Â© 2023 All Rights Reserved.</div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
